title: [Seethe Naedal, Crags]
description: Fallen stones have smashed the rock steps near the top of the crags.  However, the stones provide an easier climb then the rocky terrain surrounding the path.  Small rocks and clumps of dirt occasionally roll down the mountain, showering any unsuspecting climbers.

A silent stillness pervades the area with the coming of darkness.  Fallen stones have smashed the rock steps near the top of the crags.  However, the stones provide an easier climb then the rocky terrain surrounding the path.  Small rocks and clumps of dirt occasionally roll down the mountain, showering any unsuspecting climbers.
